Date: Sun, 25 Nov 2018 18:13:09 +0900
Subject: [PATCH 702/909] arm64: dts: renesas: r8a77965: Change default of all
 IPMMU devices to disable

commit d85c852beb841c814445a15fdb3b362e2430e7c7 from
git://git.kernel.org/pub/scm/linux/kernel/git/horms/renesas-bsp.git

This patch disables all IPMMU device defaults and maintains the same
IPMMU support environment with previous released R-Car Linux BSP.

Signed-off-by: Takeshi Kihara <takeshi.kihara.df@renesas.com>
Signed-off-by: Meng Li <Meng.Li@windriver.com>
